        "category": "classfeature",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>One of your ancestors was a mortal who mastered magic. Such magical blood can remain latent for generations, but in you it manifested in full.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> arcane</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Arcana, Society</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Detect Magic]</em>, 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Force Barrage]{Magic Missile}</em>, 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dispel Magic]</em>, 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Haste]</em>, 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Translocate]</em>, 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Scouting Eye]{Prying Eye}</em>, 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Disintegrate]</em>, 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Prismatic Spray]</em>, 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Quandary]{Maze}</em>, 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Prismatic Sphere]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Ancestral Memories]</em>, advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Extend Spell]</em>, greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Arcane Countermeasure]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> A surge of ancestral memories grants you or one target a +1 status bonus to skill checks for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Imperial Blood Magic]</p>"
        },
